item.title: 40 kVA Ultra Quiet Denyo Generator
item.dc:creator: hadimarashy
item.description:
Our ‘Ultra Quiet Denyo’ 40kVA Power Generators, have become a firm favourite with our event & construction customers. They are often referred to as “Pinks” for obvious reasons. They have a robust build which means they are the perfect solution when ultra-low noise output is a must. They sit alongside our Fusteq sets as an alternative “silenced” solution.
